<br>
Then do PA on -0- Gray with same weapon. Get yy damage. Subtract xx damage from above.<br>
<br>
Change weapons and repeat.<br>
<br>
Buff QUI and repeat.<br>
<br>
Buff Haste and repeat. <br>
<br>
Hrm, yes I forgot that Skill in a Weapon doesn't change PA damage. Easy to test ofcourse. PA a level -0- Gray with a Blade, then do it with a Pierce. Same Damage.<br>
<br>
Here are the results of the test I had a rogue do:<br>
<br>
1.5DPS 2.4 SPD Sword: Base Damage 11, Total 446, PA 435.<br>
1.5DPS 2.3 SPD Dagger: Base Damage 10, Total 445, PA 435.<br>
15.6DPS 5.0 SPD Staff: Base Damage 225, Total 661, PA 436.<br>
14.1DPS 2.3 SPD Epic Dagger: Base Damage 98, Total 534, PA 436.<br>
<br>
When you repeat the tests by buffing QUI or Haste you see no change in PA damage or Base Damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvalarauco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valarauco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 2:51:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2070.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~bdemong/valaface.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Irrelevant but in case you care, both those weapons are +4 pierce. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 10:39:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2070.topic&index=17>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Val, out of curiosity what was your base damage and total damage with each weapon? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uubergnome563.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ubergnome563</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 1:18:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2070.t