<br>
You preform peforate artery perfecly(+2100)<br>
you hit grey for 680<br>
<br>
w/o quick<br>
<br>
and <br>
<br>
You preform peforate artery perfectly(+1000)<br>
You hit grey for 680<br>
<br>
The difference being (this was posted by somebody before) that quickness/haste lowers the bonus damage you recieve per style in exchance for faster melee.<br>
<br>
On a yellow you wont get bonuses that exceed your cap, so this may be more noticable.<br>
